strings.Value: "How about this: you pretend you didn't notice anyone, and I'll spare your lives."
"How dare you! I'm an honored guest of His Highness, and he invited me here!"
"Well, looks like I've been caught... But wouldn't you prefer to spend your time counting this thousand gold I have, rather than rush off to turn me in?"
[Attack] "You should have looked the other way."
"I'm aware. He's the one who invited me."
"Back off peacefully, or I'll make you do so."
"Perhaps a thousand gold will persuade you to let me in?"
"I think I must be lost. I'll just be going."
"Hey! You can't be here! This is High Highness King Irovetti's camp!"
"Hey, who's crawling around there? Stand still, hands in the air!"
"What's this, a bribe? Not a chance. Thieves! Raise the alarm!"
"Is that a threat?! Raise the alarm!"
"Don't try to confuse us! We'll hand you over to the king and let him decide what to do with you!"
"We're not supposed to allow anyone in! If the king commands it, we will, but at this point you could be a thief for all we know!"
